items.name: Villains Wiki
items.title: Villains Wiki
items.headline: Villains Wiki
items.desc: Villains Wiki is dedicated to creating a database of villains from all media, ranging from cartoons to movies, books, video games and comics. Without the villain, there is rarely a plot, and this wiki aims to showcase the characters we all love to hate.

items.name: Wickedpedia
items.title: Wickedpedia
items.headline: Wickedpedia, the Disney Villains Wiki
items.desc: Welcome, foolish mortals, to Wickedpedia, the wiki about the Disney Villains that anyone can edit, including mere humans like you. Whether you're a fan of Maleficent, Ursula, Scar, or any other villain in the Disney mythology, this is the wiki where you can share your knowledge and passion with your fellow fans. Join us today... if you dare!

items.name: Real Life Villains Wiki
items.title: Real Life Villains Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to the Real Life Villains Wiki
items.desc:
This wiki is about all the general evil villains of real life history, from Hitler to Osama bin Laden, from dictators to fanatics, and from early history through to modern day villains.

Our wiki is open to be edited by anyone - please do join and help expand our wiki with new information and villains!
